\section{Technical Notes}
\label{sec:technotessec}

Data on radon tests and mean concentrations was obtained from the CDC National Public Health Environmental Tracking Network via the Tracking API \cite{CDCEpi,mcgeehin2004national}. Census data for housing-unit adjusted comparisons were obtained from the U.S. census via the \texttt{tidycensus} package for R version 4.1.2 \cite{R-cite, R-tidycensus}. Full code and tabular versions of the data are available at {\color{red}{(insert GitHub URL)}}


